public class ServerEventController
extends ServerEventControllerMVC

The ServerEventController provides registration with the GWT Event Services for your application. When you indicate that your controller/view handles an MvcServerEvent, the MVC framework automatically generates code to register the component with the server event controller. Events for objects of the specified class are then forwarded to the component automatically.
